# ARKHOS Roadmap

Живой документ развития системы. DataviewJS рендерит dashboard, агенты ищут через QMD.

## How to use

**Добавить фичу:** вставь блок в нужную секцию:
```
#### Feature Name
[feature:: Name] [status:: planned] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P2]
Описание фичи для агентов и поиска.
```

**Статусы:** `done` | `active` | `planned` | `idea`
**Домены:** `infra` | `studiokook` | `ai-gen` | `cross`
**Приоритеты:** `P0` (critical) | `P1` (high) | `P2` (medium) | `P3` (low)

---

## Dashboard

```dataviewjs
const content = await dv.io.load(dv.current().file.path);
const lines = content.split('\n');
const features = [];
const re = /\[feature:: (.+?)\].*\[status:: (.+?)\].*\[domain:: (.+?)\].*\[priority:: (.+?)\]/;
const dateRe = /\[completed:: (.+?)\]/;

let inCodeBlock = false;
for (const line of lines) {
  if (line.trim().startsWith('```')) { inCodeBlock = !inCodeBlock; continue; }
  if (inCodeBlock) continue;
  const m = line.match(re);
  if (m) {
    const d = line.match(dateRe);
    features.push({ feature: m[1], status: m[2], domain: m[3], priority: m[4], completed: d ? d[1] : '' });
  }
}

const active = features.filter(f => f.status === 'active').sort((a,b) => a.priority.localeCompare(b.priority));
const planned = features.filter(f => f.status === 'planned').sort((a,b) => a.priority.localeCompare(b.priority));
const ideas = features.filter(f => f.status === 'idea');
const done = features.filter(f => f.status === 'done').sort((a,b) => (b.completed || '').localeCompare(a.completed || ''));
const recent = done.filter(f => {
  if (!f.completed) return false;
  const diff = (Date.now() - new Date(f.completed).getTime()) / 86400000;
  return diff <= 30;
});

dv.header(3, `🔨 Active (${active.length})`);
if (active.length) dv.table(['Feature', 'Domain', 'P'], active.map(f => [f.feature, f.domain, f.priority]));
else dv.paragraph('*No active features*');

dv.header(3, `📋 Planned (${planned.length})`);
if (planned.length) dv.table(['Feature', 'Domain', 'P'], planned.map(f => [f.feature, f.domain, f.priority]));
else dv.paragraph('*No planned features*');

dv.header(3, `💡 Ideas (${ideas.length})`);
if (ideas.length) dv.table(['Feature', 'Domain', 'P'], ideas.map(f => [f.feature, f.domain, f.priority]));

dv.header(3, `✅ Done recently (${recent.length}/${done.length} total)`);
if (recent.length) dv.table(['Feature', 'Domain', 'Date'], recent.map(f => [f.feature, f.domain, f.completed]));
```

