## Features

---

### Core Infrastructure

#### Ghost Session Memory

[feature:: Ghost Session Memory] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P0] [completed:: 2026-03-19]
Система памяти между сессиями. Ghost CLI + MCP deep_search. Хранит decisions, mistakes, knowledge, strategies. Автоматический inject релевантного контекста в новые сессии по file overlap.

#### Session Audit Pipeline

[feature:: Session Audit Pipeline] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P0] [completed:: 2026-03-19]
PreCompact hook: Sonnet 4.6 анализирует транскрипт → errors в vault troubleshooting, patterns в vault global-patterns, facts в MEMORY.md. Upsert по ключам, без дубликатов. 424 turns обработано в первый запуск.

#### Hooks Pipeline v2

[feature:: Hooks Pipeline v2] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P0] [completed:: 2026-03-29]
12 активных hooks: SessionStart, Stop (trace-collector + pattern-detector + output-critic enforcement), PreCompact (session-audit + ghost-finalize), UserPromptSubmit (compact-report-injector + auto-search), StopFailure, FileChanged, TaskCreated. Shared modules в hooks/shared/.

#### Output-Critic Enforcement

[feature:: Output-Critic Enforcement] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P0] [completed:: 2026-03-28]
Stop hook type:prompt — отдельная модель оценивает output, возвращает `{ok: false}` если critic не применён. Единственный надёжный enforcement mechanism в Claude Code.

#### QMD Semantic Search

[feature:: QMD Semantic Search] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P1] [completed:: 2026-03-20]
BM25 search по vault и ghost коллекциям. Auto-search worker при каждом промпте (timeout 3s, min 25 chars). Fallback от vsearch (vector, CMake issues на VPS).

#### Compact Report Delivery

[feature:: Compact Report Delivery] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P1] [completed:: 2026-03-29]
Отчёт session-audit доставляется через PENDING блок в MEMORY.md (native auto-memory). Claude видит, выводит в чат, удаляет. Dual delivery: file + MEMORY.md.

#### Shared Hook Modules

[feature:: Shared Hook Modules] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P2] [completed:: 2026-03-29]
`hooks/shared/paths.js` (CLAUDE_DIR, VAULT_DIR, QMD) + `hooks/shared/obsidian-api.js` (callHaiku/callSonnet, appendToVault, sendTelegram). Устраняет дублирование кода между hooks.

#### VPS Full Setup

[feature:: VPS Full Setup] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P1] [completed:: 2026-03-28]
Claude CLI 2.1.86 на Hetzner (157.180.33.253). Ghost hooks, MEMORY paths, permissions, UFW, FireCrawl MCP. tmux bridge с 4h auto-rotation.

#### Tracker DB

[feature:: Tracker DB] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P2] [completed:: 2026-03-19]
better-sqlite3, `~/.claude/patterns/tracker.db`. trace-collector записывает tool traces, pattern-detector ищет error patterns. 7-day rotation + WAL checkpoint.

