### Video Pipeline

#### YouTube → Obsidian Pipeline

[feature:: YouTube → Obsidian Pipeline] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P1] [completed:: 2026-03-22]
n8n workflow (23 nodes): Telegram bot → transcript (youtube-transcript-api/Whisper) → insight extraction (claude-sonnet-4-5) → 2 commits per video (raw + enriched). Auto-pull every 15min.

#### Video Insight Router

[feature:: Video Insight Router] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P2] [completed:: 2026-03-22]
Post-pull classification: Haiku vs routing-map.md → append to vault destinations. Dedup ~56%. Idempotent via routed:true frontmatter.

#### Pattern Analyzer

[feature:: Pattern Analyzer] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P2] [completed:: 2026-03-22]
Post-routing Sonnet analysis: convergence/gap/actionable/staleness/optimization patterns. Telegram alerts (critical), Obsidian tasks (medium). 7-day cooldown anti-spam.

#### Video Service (VPS)

[feature:: Video Service VPS] [status:: done] [domain:: infra] [priority:: P2] [completed:: 2026-03-22]
Python HTTP sidecar port 3001. youtube-transcript-api + yt-dlp + Whisper API fallback. Systemd service, UFW docker-only.

